rges’s more general involvement in the publishing industry influenced not only his formation as a writer, but also global book markets and reading practices in world literature. In this way it tells the story of Borges’s profound efforts to revolutionize and revitalize literature in Latin America through his varying jobs in the publishing industry.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Sep 2021) 0aAuthors, Latin AmericanvBiography. 0aBooks and readingzLatin America. 0aPublishers and publishingzLatin America. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / Caribbean & Latin American.2bisacsh40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300262407423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300262407/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles